The paper deals with image dataset construction, which is a topic related to computer vision (cs.CV). The authors also mention the use of web images and semantic descriptions, which suggests a connection to information retrieval (cs.IR) and natural language processing (cs.CL). Additionally, the paper discusses multi-instance learning, which is a subfield of machine learning (cs.LG) and has applications in multimedia analysis (cs.MM).
